</figcaption>
</figure><!-- media__figure -->

<div class="media__content h-card h-card--staff">
<div class="p-name">Roland Sinker</div>
<div class="p-job-title">Acting Chief Executive</div>
<p class="secondary">Roland joined the Trust in 2005 as Director of Strategy for King&#8217;s and latterly as Chief Operating Officer. Prior to joining the NHS, Roland worked as a lawyer and management consultant.</p>
<p class="secondary">Roland is a director and company secretary of KCH Commercial Services.</p>

</div><!-- media__content -->
