<div class="media__content h-card h-card--staff">
<div class="p-name">Michael Marrinan</div>
<div class="p-job-title">Medical Director</div>
<p class="secondary">Michael is a consultant thoracic surgeon and was appointed as the Trust&#8217;s Medical Director in February 2010 following two years' service as Deputy Medical Director.</p>
<p class="secondary">Michael has worked at King&#8217;s for nearly 20 years, and has previously chaired both the Consultants&#8217; Committee and the Patient Records Committee. He was also heavily involved in the development of King&#8217;s activity based costing system.</p>

